Package: mcSEM
Type: Package
Title: Monte Carlo Sample Size Estimation for Structural Equation Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your Name", "Your Last Name",
                  email = "your.email@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Monte Carlo simulation-based sample size estimation for
    Confirmatory Factor Analysis (CFA), Exploratory Factor Analysis (EFA),
    and Structural Equation Models (SEM). Supports both a priori (before
    data collection) and a posteriori (with existing data) analyses.
    Handles ordinal/Likert data with WLSMV estimator and polychoric
    correlations. Evaluates power based on CFI, RMSEA, and SRMR fit indices.
